WEBVTT

00:01.068 --> 00:02.536
<i>PREVIOUSLY ON "WEEDS"...</i>

00:02.569 --> 00:05.038
PEOPLE SEEM TO LIKE
WHAT WE'RE SELLING.

00:05.072 --> 00:07.774
MILF WEED ‐‐
IT'S THE BRAND OF THE DAY.

00:07.808 --> 00:09.209
EVERYBODY
LOVE THAT SHIT, TOO.

00:09.243 --> 00:13.113
YOU WILL NOTICE ABOVE ME
OUR VERY FIRST CAMERA.

00:13.146 --> 00:15.349
DRUGS ARE WRONG!

00:15.382 --> 00:18.919
I THINK YOU'RE TURNING AGRESTIC
INTO A POLICE STATE.

00:18.952 --> 00:20.487
[ CHILDREN CHEERING ]

00:20.521 --> 00:21.755
I TOTALLY KICK ASS.

00:21.788 --> 00:23.123
YOU WANT ME
TO BE YOUR GIRLFRIEND?

00:23.156 --> 00:26.026
Andy: THEY THINK HE'S COOL
SINCE HE TOOK UP YOUR CAUSE.

00:26.059 --> 00:28.662
WHAT CAUSE?
"GO, DRUGS! RAH RAH RAH!"

00:28.695 --> 00:30.297
CAN I COME IN?
BAD TIMING.

00:30.330 --> 00:32.199
IT'S DAD'S BIRTHDAY,
FOR FUCK'S SAKE.

00:32.232 --> 00:34.601
WE'RE MARRIED.
IT'S A BUSINESS ARRANGEMENT.

00:35.936 --> 00:37.471
WHAT WAS THAT?

00:37.504 --> 00:39.173
I DON'T KNOW.

00:41.041 --> 00:43.010
YOUR BOYS AT THE D. E. A. ‐‐
DO THEY KNOW ABOUT ME?

00:43.043 --> 00:44.344
PROBABLY NOT.
YOU'RE SMALL‐TIME.

00:44.378 --> 00:46.046
Nancy: I THOUGHT
WE WERE UNDER YOUR RADAR.

00:46.079 --> 00:48.081
AND SINCE I'M KEEPING
YOU THERE,

00:48.115 --> 00:50.384
I GOT TO SHOW MY BOSS
SOME RESULTS.

00:50.417 --> 00:52.920
DON'T MOVE!
NOBODY FUCKING MOVE!

00:52.953 --> 00:54.688
THIS IS A HOUSE
OF WORSHIP.

00:54.721 --> 00:57.191
DID YOU TELL HEYLIA
OR DID YOU HAVE CONRAD DO IT?

00:57.224 --> 00:58.392
YOU JUST WOULDN'T LISTEN.

00:58.425 --> 01:00.827
Heylia: YOU WENT OFF
WITH ONE OF MY CUSTOMERS

01:00.861 --> 01:03.864
AND CREATED A NEW GAME
BEHIND MY BACK.

01:03.897 --> 01:04.932
SHE'S NOT GONNA STAY MAD.

01:04.965 --> 01:06.867
YOU DO NOT KNOW HEYLIA.

01:06.900 --> 01:08.402
♪♪ BA‐DO‐WOP ♪♪

01:08.435 --> 01:11.839
