01:11.872 --> 01:14.808
♪♪ LITTLE BOXES ON THE HILLSIDE ♪♪

01:14.842 --> 01:17.845
♪♪ LITTLE BOXES
MADE OF TICKY‐TACKY ♪♪

01:17.878 --> 01:20.347
♪♪ LITTLE BOXES ON THE HILLSIDE ♪♪

01:20.380 --> 01:23.884
♪♪ LITTLE BOXES ALL THE SAME ♪♪

01:23.917 --> 01:26.620
♪♪ THERE'S A GREEN ONE
AND A PINK ONE ♪♪

01:26.653 --> 01:29.590
♪♪ AND A BLUE ONE
AND A YELLOW ONE ♪♪

01:29.623 --> 01:32.826
♪♪ AND THEY'RE ALL MADE
OUT OF TICKY‐TACKY ♪♪

01:32.860 --> 01:36.096
♪♪ AND THEY ALL LOOK
JUST THE SAME ♪♪

01:36.129 --> 01:38.799
♪♪ AND THE PEOPLE IN THE HOUSES ♪♪

01:38.832 --> 01:42.402
♪♪ ALL WENT TO THE UNIVERSITY ♪♪

01:42.436 --> 01:45.172
♪♪ WHERE THEY WERE PUT IN BOXES ♪♪

01:45.205 --> 01:48.308
♪♪ AND THEY ALL CAME OUT
THE SAME ♪♪

01:48.342 --> 01:51.912
♪♪ AND THERE'S DOCTORS
AND LAWYERS ♪♪

01:51.945 --> 01:55.382
♪♪ AND BUSINESS EXECUTIVES ♪♪

01:55.415 --> 01:58.585
♪♪ AND THEY'RE ALL MADE OUT
OF TICKY‐TACKY ♪♪

01:58.619 --> 02:03.590
♪♪ AND THEY ALL LOOK
JUST THE SAME ♪♪

02:03.624 --> 02:08.896
ALL STARTS HERE
UNDER A BEAUTIFUL, BLUE SKY.

02:08.929 --> 02:11.598
"THAT'S MINE."
"NO, IT AIN'T."

02:11.632 --> 02:12.533
"YES, IT IS."

02:12.566 --> 02:17.538
THIS IS WHERE YOU FIND OUT
WHO YOU ARE.

02:17.571 --> 02:22.876
YOU GONNA PUSH,
OR YOU GONNA GET PUSHED?

02:22.910 --> 02:25.379
SO WHICH ONE YOU THINK
GONNA WIN?

02:25.412 --> 02:26.813
FAT ONE.

02:26.847 --> 02:29.049
HE GOT MORE LEVERAGE...

02:29.082 --> 02:30.751
UNLESS THE OTHER ONE
BITES HIM.

02:30.784 --> 02:31.919
THEN IT'S ANYONE'S GAME.

02:31.952 --> 02:34.288
I GOT HERE
AS SOON AS I COULD.

02:34.321 --> 02:37.891
THIS IS NOT OFF THE FREEWAY.
YOU MAKE A LEFT...

02:37.925 --> 02:39.860
WE DON'T KNOW YOU.

02:39.893 --> 02:41.695
SIT YOUR PRETTY ASS
ON OVER THERE

02:41.728 --> 02:42.996
AND STARE OFF SOMEWHERE ELSE.

02:43.030 --> 02:46.066
WOULDN'T WANT THE GOOD MEN
PARKED OVER IN THE CHEVY

02:46.099 --> 02:49.136
THINKING YOU'S SOMETHING OTHER
THAN WHAT YOU LOOK LIKE.

02:49.169 --> 02:50.537
BITCH IN
WAY OVER HER HEAD.

02:50.571 --> 02:54.408
YEAH, THAT'S WHAT HAPPENS
WHEN YOU GET RAIDED.

02:54.441 --> 02:57.878
YOU GET TWO WHITE BOYS
IN AN IMPALA

02:57.911 --> 03:00.380
FOLLOWING YOU
EVERYWHERE YOU GO.

03:00.414 --> 03:01.381
[ CHUCKLES ]

03:01.415 --> 03:04.318
BUT SHE DON'T HAVE TO
WORRY ABOUT THAT,

03:04.351 --> 03:06.320
DO SHE, LeVAN?

03:06.353 --> 03:07.721
NO, SHE DON'T,

03:07.754 --> 03:10.858
'CAUSE SHE WENT OFF AND MARRIED
HERSELF A D. E. A. AGENT.

03:10.891 --> 03:12.092
YES, SHE DID ‐‐

03:12.125 --> 03:14.995
SHIPPED OFF SOME ARMENIANS
AND STARTED FARMING.

03:15.028 --> 03:17.931
CAN YOU BELIEVE THAT?
CAN YOU BELIEVE THAT?

03:17.965 --> 03:21.134
I HAD NO CHOICE,
AND I WARNED YOU ABOUT THE BUST.

03:21.168 --> 03:23.403
AM I SUPPOSED TO SAY
"THANK YOU"?

03:23.437 --> 03:27.140
YOU SHUT ME DOWN.
AIN'T NOTHING COMING IN NOW.

03:27.174 --> 03:28.842
WE CAN HELP YOU GET BY

03:28.876 --> 03:31.812
WHILE YOU GET YOURSELF
UP AND RUNNING AGAIN.

03:31.845 --> 03:34.882
SHE DID NOT
JUST SAY THAT.

03:34.915 --> 03:37.484
YOU TOOK AWAY
MY LIVELIHOOD.

03:37.518 --> 03:41.455
NOW, YOU THINK YOUR HELP
GONNA MAKE THAT RIGHT?

03:41.488 --> 03:44.725
NO, IT'S JUST THE BITCH
IN WAY OVER HER HEAD TALKING.

03:44.758 --> 03:46.260
WHAT DO YOU
WANT ME TO DO?

03:46.293 --> 03:48.462
YOU START BY TALKING
TO YOUR HUSBAND.

03:48.495 --> 03:50.931
YOU GONNA HAVE TO DO
WHATEVER IT TAKES.

03:50.964 --> 03:52.266
AND IF THAT MEANS

03:52.299 --> 03:55.936
YOU GOT TO SIT ON HIS FACE
WITH ROSES UP YOUR SNATCH

03:55.969 --> 03:59.640
FIVE NIGHTS A WEEK,
YOU GONNA DO THAT.

03:59.673 --> 04:02.442
HELP ME.
WHO THE FUCK ARE YOU?

04:02.476 --> 04:05.212
HEY, VANEETA, WHATEVER HAPPENED
TO THAT CHILD,

04:05.245 --> 04:07.181
UM...NANCY
SOMETHING OR OTHER?

04:07.214 --> 04:10.784
AIN'T THAT THAT WHITE BITCH
THAT THOUGHT SHE WAS SOMETHING?

04:10.817 --> 04:11.985
YEAH, WHERE SHE AT NOW?

04:12.019 --> 04:14.688
SHE GONE NOW ‐‐
VANISHED.

04:14.721 --> 04:16.657
NOBODY SEEN HER SINCE.

04:16.690 --> 04:18.225
OH, MAN.

04:18.258 --> 04:20.194
THOSE POOR LITTLE BOYS.

04:20.227 --> 04:23.931
LOSING BOTH THEIR PARENTS ‐‐
AIN'T THAT SOMETHING.

04:23.964 --> 04:24.998
CAN YOU IMAGINE?

04:25.032 --> 04:27.000
OKAY, STOP IT.

04:27.034 --> 04:31.638
I WILL STOP EVERYTHING.

04:31.672 --> 04:34.775
I AM HEYLIA TURNER JAMES,

04:34.808 --> 04:36.777
AND I KNOW
WHERE YOU GROW,

04:36.810 --> 04:39.346
AND I KNOW
WHERE YOU LIVE.

04:39.379 --> 04:43.584
AND BOTH YOU AND CONRAD
ARE ON THE CLOCK

04:43.617 --> 04:45.853
TO MAKE THIS THING RIGHT.

04:45.886 --> 04:49.690
TICK‐FUCKING‐TOCK.
COME ON, LITTLE GIRL.

04:59.633 --> 05:00.868
CAPTAIN TILL?

05:00.901 --> 05:04.037
SCOTTSON, SIT DOWN.

05:04.071 --> 05:07.107
I'M REREADING
YOUR REPORT.

05:07.140 --> 05:08.809
I GOT TO TELL YOU, PETE.

05:08.842 --> 05:09.943
FIRST TIME THROUGH,

05:09.977 --> 05:12.346
IT GAVE ME THE SHITS
AND GIGGLES SO GOOD,

05:12.379 --> 05:14.915
I HAD IT LAMINATED ‐‐
ALL NINE PAGES.

05:14.948 --> 05:16.984
I'M GONNA PUT THEM UP
ON MY WALL OVER THERE.

05:17.017 --> 05:18.752
AND EVERY TIME
I'M HAVING A CRAP DAY,

05:18.785 --> 05:22.623
I'M GONNA READ ABOUT YOU
AND YOUR MUSLIM PRAYER MEETING.

05:22.656 --> 05:24.591
THE SUSPECTS
WERE TIPPED OFF.
YOU THINK?

05:24.625 --> 05:27.561
TELL ME, AGENT,
WHERE'S THE NEXT BIG BUST?

05:27.594 --> 05:30.664
OUR LADY OF THE CRACK PIPE
OR TEMPLE BETH METH?

05:30.697 --> 05:31.965
SURVEILLANCE
IS CONTINUING.

05:31.999 --> 05:33.767
MIKE AND ROBBIE
IN THE IMPALA.

05:33.800 --> 05:35.035
AND WE STILL HAVE
WIRE TAPS.

05:35.068 --> 05:37.504
AND WE'RE GONNA WAIT
FOR THE FOOD STAMPS TO RUN OUT.

05:37.538 --> 05:40.607
SHE'S AN OPEN DOOR TO U‐TURN.
I NEED SOME SLACK HERE.

05:40.641 --> 05:41.942
SHUMAN
NEEDS MIKE AND ROBBIE.

05:41.975 --> 05:43.877
CAPTAIN ‐‐
YOU GOT HOSED, PETE.

05:43.911 --> 05:45.846
WRAP IT UP.

05:45.879 --> 05:47.881
YES, SIR.

05:47.915 --> 05:52.019
IT'S MY ANNIVERSARY TODAY.
HE FORGOT.

05:52.052 --> 05:55.022
HE FORGETS
A LOT OF THINGS.

05:56.823 --> 05:58.825
17 YEARS.

05:58.859 --> 06:00.661
HMM.

06:02.462 --> 06:04.898
[ SIGHS ]
HOW LONG HAVE YOU AND ‐‐

06:04.932 --> 06:05.799
20.

06:05.832 --> 06:06.867
18.

06:06.900 --> 06:07.935
22.

06:07.968 --> 06:10.204
I'M NOT GOOD
WITH NUMBERS.

06:10.237 --> 06:11.905
YOU'RE AN ACCOUNTANT.

06:11.939 --> 06:14.808
DIFFERENT.
THOSE ARE GUY NUMBERS.

06:14.842 --> 06:17.644
YEARS MARRIED ‐‐
THAT'S GIRL MATH.

06:19.446 --> 06:22.649
I'M SEIZED WITH GUILT.
ARE YOU SEIZED WITH GUILT?

06:22.683 --> 06:24.318
SEIZED.

06:24.351 --> 06:27.120
[ GRUNTING ]

06:27.154 --> 06:28.655
[ GLASS SHATTERS ]

06:28.689 --> 06:30.824
[ BARKING ]

06:30.858 --> 06:32.759
GOOD GIRL.
GOOD GIRL.

06:32.793 --> 06:33.827
GOOD GIRL.

06:33.861 --> 06:36.396
WE SHOULDN'T
BE DOING THIS.

06:36.430 --> 06:39.433
YOU'RE RIGHT.
WE HAVE FAMILIES.

06:39.466 --> 06:40.567
CHILDREN.

06:40.601 --> 06:42.436
BEAUTIFUL CHILDREN.

06:42.469 --> 06:44.771
THIS WOULD DESTROY THEM.

06:44.805 --> 06:46.740
[ MOANING ]

06:46.773 --> 06:49.276
[ GLASS SHATTERS ]

06:49.309 --> 06:52.980
LEGENDARY!

06:54.515 --> 06:57.618
SHE THINKS I CAN
MAKE PETER DISAPPEAR.

06:57.651 --> 07:00.921
PETER WANTS HER IN JAIL,
ME OUT OF THE BUSINESS.

07:00.954 --> 07:02.122
[ SIGHS ]

07:02.155 --> 07:05.893
SILAS WANTS TO SKIP COLLEGE
AND BE LIKE ME.

07:05.926 --> 07:06.994
I THINK SHANE KNOWS WHAT I DO.

07:07.027 --> 07:08.762
I CAN'T EVEN
LOOK HIM IN THE FACE.

07:08.795 --> 07:10.597
I'VE NEVER
BEEN TO CHINA.
SIT DOWN!

07:10.631 --> 07:11.899
SHE THREATENED TO KILL ME!

07:11.932 --> 07:13.734
STOP SUCKING
ON THIS FUCKING STRAW.

07:13.767 --> 07:14.968
GIVE ME YOUR HAND.

07:15.002 --> 07:17.571
BREATHE.
LOOK AT ME.

07:17.604 --> 07:18.906
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

07:18.939 --> 07:20.374
KOREAN GIRL
TAUGHT ME THIS.

07:20.407 --> 07:23.277
KEEP BREATHING
AND LOOK AT ME.

07:25.279 --> 07:27.281
[ SIGHS ]

07:29.550 --> 07:32.753
I DON'T KNOW WHAT TO DO.

07:32.786 --> 07:34.988
I'M OUT OF MOVES.

07:35.022 --> 07:37.858
BABY, YOU NEVER HAD ANY.

07:37.891 --> 07:40.460
MOVES MEAN
YOU THINK THINGS THROUGH.

07:40.494 --> 07:42.029
YOU HAVE BEEN REACTING.

07:44.031 --> 07:46.733
THAT FEELS GOOD.

07:46.767 --> 07:48.735
YOU READY TO GET
IN THE BACKSEAT?

07:48.769 --> 07:50.737
YOU READY
FOR CONRAD'S PLAN NOW?

07:50.771 --> 07:52.840
YOU OUT.

07:52.873 --> 07:54.641
I'm out.

07:54.675 --> 07:57.544
YOU DUG YOURSELF A PIT
A MILE DEEP AND A FOOT WIDE,

07:57.578 --> 08:00.314
AND YOU'RE LOOKING BACK UP
AT A PINHOLE.

08:00.347 --> 08:01.415
YOU OUT.

08:06.620 --> 08:08.455
Yeah.

08:08.488 --> 08:10.924
YOU GO TO HIM.
YOU TELL HIM YOU LOVE HIM.

08:10.958 --> 08:13.026
TELL HIM YOU'RE OUT
AFTER THIS HARVEST.

08:13.060 --> 08:14.428
YOU GET YOUR MONEY BACK.

08:14.461 --> 08:16.430
HEYLIA JAMES GETS WIPED OFF
HIS BOARD.

08:16.463 --> 08:18.565
I TAKE THE EQUIPMENT
AND DISAPPEAR.

08:20.567 --> 08:21.835
I'M SORRY.

08:21.869 --> 08:23.837
NO, I DON'T REALLY
WANT TO HEAR THAT.

08:23.871 --> 08:25.939
NO, NO, LISTEN.
YOU'VE BEEN A GOOD FRIEND.

08:25.973 --> 08:28.175
NO, THIS AIN'T
NO "DRIVING MISS DAISY."

08:28.208 --> 08:30.978
I AIN'T ABOUT TO FEED YOU
NO THANKSGIVING PIE.

08:32.246 --> 08:35.549
THINGS WORK OUT WITH PETER,
YOU GET YOUR MONEY.

08:37.284 --> 08:38.418
[ CLANG ]

08:38.452 --> 08:40.454
YOU DONE.

08:43.690 --> 08:45.826
YOU LOVE HIM?

08:45.859 --> 08:47.961
WHO?

08:47.995 --> 08:49.496
AGENT WONDER BREAD.

08:51.532 --> 08:53.534
I'M NOT SURE.

08:53.567 --> 08:55.002
YOU THINK YOU COULD?

08:58.972 --> 09:00.841
YOU'RE OUT?

09:00.874 --> 09:02.609
THE HOURS SUCK.

09:02.643 --> 09:05.913
THERE'S NO
HEALTH INSURANCE.

09:05.946 --> 09:09.750
IT'S A BAD JOB
FOR A DANGER JUNKIE.

09:09.783 --> 09:11.318
AND THAT'S YOU.

09:11.351 --> 09:14.755
I ADMIT I HAVE A PROBLEM.
I'M GOING COLD TURKEY.

09:14.788 --> 09:16.690
I'M SKEPTICAL.
LET ME CONVINCE YOU.

09:16.723 --> 09:19.893
COME TO DINNER TOMORROW NIGHT.
EAT WITH MY FAMILY.

09:19.927 --> 09:22.729
YOUR SONS? I DON'T KNOW
HOW THRILLED THEY'LL BE.

09:22.763 --> 09:24.398
THEY'RE GOOD KIDS.
I KNOW THAT.

09:24.431 --> 09:26.466
AND YOU'RE AMAZING.
EAT WITH US.

09:28.302 --> 09:30.204
HEYLIA WALKS,
CONRAD LEAVES?

09:30.237 --> 09:31.872
I WANT TO
MAKE A GO OF IT.

09:31.905 --> 09:33.340
DINNER?

09:33.373 --> 09:34.675
MY PLACE.

09:34.708 --> 09:36.910
BRING A TOOTHBRUSH.
[ LAUGHS ]

09:36.944 --> 09:38.846
I'M STAYING THE NIGHT?

09:38.879 --> 09:41.381
PETER IS MY BOYFRIEND.

09:42.683 --> 09:43.917
HE MAKES ME HAPPY.

09:43.951 --> 09:45.519
JUST YOUR BOYFRIEND?

09:45.552 --> 09:48.922
AND HE'S IN SOME SORT
OF LAW ENFORCEMENT, I HEAR.

09:48.956 --> 09:50.324
SO WE CAN ALL FEEL SAFE.

09:51.525 --> 09:54.161
I'VE INVITED HIM OVER
FOR DINNER TOMORROW NIGHT.

09:54.194 --> 09:55.329
IT NEEDS TO GO WELL.

09:55.362 --> 09:57.798
CAN I INVITE GRETCHEN?
ABSOLUTELY.

09:57.831 --> 09:59.833
WHAT IS THIS
WE'RE HAVING?

09:59.867 --> 10:01.502
IT'S PAELLA.

10:01.535 --> 10:02.636
RIGHT.
IT'S PRETTY.

10:02.669 --> 10:05.772
I WANT YOU TO MAKE THIS AGAIN
TOMORROW NIGHT.

10:05.806 --> 10:07.808
[ DOORBELL RINGS ]
I CAN MAKE ‐‐

10:07.841 --> 10:09.977
NO. I WANT YOU
TO MAKE THIS.

10:10.010 --> 10:11.545
YOU GOT IT.

10:11.578 --> 10:14.047
KAT!

10:14.081 --> 10:15.849
YOU LOST YOUR CAT?

10:15.883 --> 10:18.519
I'M KAT.
YOU'RE NANCY, RIGHT?

10:18.552 --> 10:19.887
I AM.

10:19.920 --> 10:21.855
THERE'S A SMELL.

10:21.889 --> 10:23.657
GRAPE JELLY?

10:23.690 --> 10:25.692
NO, IT'S FISH.

10:25.726 --> 10:27.561
OH, THAT'S ME.
THAT'S ME.

10:27.594 --> 10:29.029
IT'S SOCKEYE SALMON.

10:29.062 --> 10:31.932
DO YOU WANT SOME?
NO, I'M GOOD.

10:31.965 --> 10:33.600
WHO ARE YOU?
WHAT DO YOU WANT?

10:33.634 --> 10:35.669
IS ANDY HERE?

10:35.702 --> 10:37.971
MOM, UNCLE ANDY'S
CHOKING!

10:38.005 --> 10:39.473
COME ON IN.

10:39.506 --> 10:41.808
I'VE BEEN EATING NOTHING
BUT SOCKEYE SALMON

10:41.842 --> 10:43.177
FOR THE PAST 47 HOURS.

10:43.210 --> 10:46.547
THE MapQuest PRINTOUT SAID
IT TOOK 43, WHICH IS BULLSHIT.

10:46.580 --> 10:49.316
I MEAN, HORSE APPLES.
YOU MUST BE SHANE.

10:49.349 --> 10:51.785
HI, HEART HUG.
SAT SARI AKAR.

10:51.818 --> 10:53.820
ARE YOU THE CRAZY CHICK
FROM ALASKA

10:53.854 --> 10:55.022
WHO TRIED
TO KILL MY UNCLE?

10:55.055 --> 10:57.491
THAT IS A GREAT STORY.
HI, SILAS.

10:57.524 --> 10:59.626
YOU DROVE HERE
ALL THE WAY FROM ALASKA?

10:59.660 --> 11:02.763
I BORROWED SOME SALMON
FROM THE FISHERY.
THAT MEANS SHE STOLE IT.

11:02.796 --> 11:06.099
THE MAN AT THE 7‐ELEVEN
GAVE ME A CASE OF RED BULL.
THAT MEANS SHE STOLE IT.

11:06.133 --> 11:09.002
THAT'S ALL I'VE BEEN EATING
AND DRINKING FOR 47 HOURS.

11:09.036 --> 11:10.737
I DROVE
AND I DROVE AND I DROVE

11:10.771 --> 11:12.506
TILL I HIT THE INTERSTATE 5,

11:12.539 --> 11:16.577
AND THAT'S A STRAIGHT LINE
FOR 1,211 MILES,

11:16.610 --> 11:18.312
BUT I KNEW A SHORTCUT.

11:18.345 --> 11:19.580
HI.

11:19.613 --> 11:20.581
HI.

11:20.614 --> 11:21.582
[ LAUGHS ]

11:21.615 --> 11:22.916
HOW'D YOU FIND ME?

11:22.950 --> 11:26.920
I READ ABOUT YOUR TOE ACCIDENT
ONLINE ‐‐ GOOGLE.

11:26.954 --> 11:28.755
I MISSED YOU SO MUCH.

11:30.057 --> 11:31.892
I'M TIRED.

11:31.925 --> 11:34.895
FRESNO'S BEAUTIFUL.

11:34.928 --> 11:37.898
I WROTE A BOOK.

11:37.931 --> 11:39.900
AND SHE IS?

11:39.933 --> 11:41.735
GONE BY TOMORROW.
PROMISE.

11:41.768 --> 11:44.037
THANK YOU.

11:45.906 --> 11:48.876
HOW WAS YOUR DAY?

11:48.909 --> 11:51.645
HOW WAS MY DAY?

11:51.678 --> 11:53.914
IT WAS SWELL.

11:53.947 --> 11:56.950
HOW WAS YOUR DAY?

11:56.984 --> 12:00.053
ISABEL HAD A CALLBACK
FOR A VOICE‐OVER AUDITION.

12:00.087 --> 12:02.222
I DIDN'T LIKE
THE MATERIAL.

12:02.256 --> 12:03.257
HUH.

12:03.290 --> 12:06.126
I STOPPED BY DOUG'S OFFICE,
BUT HE WASN'T THERE ‐‐

12:06.159 --> 12:07.728
STILL TRYING
TO PATCH THINGS UP.

12:07.761 --> 12:11.164
GOOD LUCK WITH THAT.

12:14.701 --> 12:16.703
DEAN, WE HAVE TO TALK.

12:16.737 --> 12:19.139
[ CHUCKLES ]
